PAULA: What are sunnies?

02:12.416 --> 02:15.375
KAI:<i> Well, they're shells.</i>
<i>Pretty shells.</i>

02:15.458 --> 02:16.791
<i>I'll find you one later.</i>

02:18.416 --> 02:20.333
Then we'd go back to our patch

02:20.416 --> 02:24.291
and clear the waterways,
feed the pigs, pull the taro.

02:24.375 --> 02:26.000
(LAUGHS)

02:27.416 --> 02:29.000
What?

02:29.083 --> 02:32.916
I don't know, you're just...
you're so real.

02:34.416 --> 02:35.416
I'm very real.

02:40.041 --> 02:41.833
Was the hotel here?

02:41.916 --> 02:44.958
Well, they were the ones
that actually evicted us

02:45.041 --> 02:47.291
from our lo'i.
The land that was given

02:47.375 --> 02:49.666
by King Kamehameha
to the konohiki,

02:49.750 --> 02:52.416
it was a sacred title.
Can't be broken.

02:54.250 --> 02:56.625
But the government,

02:56.708 --> 02:58.750
they terminated
our lease illegally.

03:01.250 --> 03:02.708
That's fucked up.

03:02.791 --> 03:05.333
My brothers, they're still
trying to fight the county,

03:05.416 --> 03:08.250
but they can't afford a lawyer.

03:08.333 --> 03:10.291
The good ones are too expensive.

03:11.458 --> 03:13.541
(SIGHS)
It's a shit situation.

03:15.125 --> 03:18.000
And now you work for the same
assholes that stole from you?

03:19.583 --> 03:22.625
When my brothers found out
that I took this job...

03:24.083 --> 03:25.458
they were so pissed.

03:27.583 --> 03:31.166
But I gotta make a living,
you know?

03:49.166 --> 03:51.791
I have to go
before she wakes up.

03:51.875 --> 03:54.375
Why don't you want her to know
that we're hanging out?

03:57.375 --> 03:58.416
She's tricky.

03:59.958 --> 04:01.291
Isn't she your friend?

04:01.958 --> 04:03.541
Yeah, she's my friend.

04:05.166 --> 04:07.541
As long as she has more
of everything than I do.

04:09.916 --> 04:13.833
But if I have something
of my own, she wants it.

04:14.916 --> 04:17.291
(LAUGHS)
She's like that, huh?

04:22.708 --> 04:24.458
That family is crazy.

04:26.083 --> 04:30.125
Oh, my God. (LAUGHS)
You wouldn't even believe it.

04:30.208 --> 04:31.958
All these guests are crazy.

04:32.041 --> 04:35.666
