06:34.416 --> 06:38.583
The whole thing with Lani put me
on edge, so I took a Xanax.

06:38.666 --> 06:42.041
But then I was, um, dragging,
so I took an upper.

06:44.625 --> 06:46.791
And then I took another
and then another.

06:49.291 --> 06:50.916
Then I went down
to the bar after work

06:51.000 --> 06:52.708
-and had a few shots.
-Armond.

06:52.791 --> 06:57.333
