07:03.500 --> 07:05.000
(SIGHS)

07:05.083 --> 07:07.666
But this is why
I have to stay sober, Belinda,

07:07.750 --> 07:08.958
because when I dabble...

07:10.083 --> 07:11.416
even just a little...

07:12.583 --> 07:14.833
I fall completely off the beam.

07:14.916 --> 07:16.166
Sounds like it.

07:16.250 --> 07:17.833
But I'm-- I'm okay.

07:17.916 --> 07:20.583
I'm-- I'm not going
down that road again.

07:20.666 --> 07:23.583
Then get rid of the pills.

07:23.666 --> 07:25.875
Absolutely. Hundred percent.

07:26.625 --> 07:29.541
