07:42.291 --> 07:43.666
I did scuba.

07:43.750 --> 07:45.916
Mm-hmm.
And the eight hours after that?

07:47.541 --> 07:49.250
I drank beer at the Kahuna.

07:49.333 --> 07:52.583
Mm. Well, we ended up
eating dinner at the restaurant.

07:52.666 --> 07:54.208
It wasn't very festive.

07:54.291 --> 07:56.916
I'm sorry. I was depressed.

07:58.125 --> 08:02.333
I kept thinking about
how my dad chose his sex life

08:02.416 --> 08:04.291
over his family.

08:04.375 --> 08:05.875
Well, that sounds familiar.

08:10.125 --> 08:11.875
And it literally killed him.

08:13.833 --> 08:16.375
So I never really got
to know him, you know?

08:17.416 --> 08:19.500
(SIGHS)

08:19.583 --> 08:23.083
Well, are you gonna
participate today,

08:23.166 --> 08:24.791
or are you gonna go
on another bender?

08:24.875 --> 08:26.458
Participate!

08:27.666 --> 08:29.000
Happy, happy.

08:31.000 --> 08:32.208
Jesus Christ.

08:34.625 --> 08:35.666
Girls!

08:38.750 --> 08:40.416
All right, girls,
let's get breakfast.

08:42.416 --> 08:45.500
The buffet is expensive,
and we've already paid for it.

08:45.583 --> 08:48.541
Mom, Paula can't keep eating
this much fruit.

08:48.625 --> 08:49.708
