08:51.958 --> 08:52.958
Oh, my God.

08:53.041 --> 08:54.750
OLIVIA MOSSBACHER:
She keeps getting diarrhea.

08:54.833 --> 08:55.916
And cramps.

08:56.000 --> 08:59.541
Eat some meat, Paula.
Eat a sausage. I don't know.

08:59.625 --> 09:01.750
Did Quinn sleep on the beach
again last night?

09:01.833 --> 09:04.250
This is not okay.
You've got to be more protective

09:04.333 --> 09:06.333
of your younger brother, Olivia.

09:06.416 --> 09:08.125
You can't just make him sleep
on the beach

09:08.208 --> 09:10.041
where he can be
washed away with the tides.

09:10.125 --> 09:13.625
Yeah, Olivia, he could've been
kidnapped by butt pirates.

09:13.708 --> 09:16.416
Or end up in a bukkake
with a pod of dolphins.

09:17.000 --> 09:18.666
(GIRLS SNICKERING)

09:20.375 --> 09:22.500
(WAVES CRASHING)

