11:29.833 --> 11:33.041
I think you're great.
But I know what you mean.

11:35.416 --> 11:36.583
Um...

11:36.666 --> 11:40.708
Maybe I just don't have, like,
the drive like some people.

11:40.791 --> 11:43.875
And I'm worried that now
it's just gonna get worse.

11:43.958 --> 11:46.208
