Just be serious.

11:49.750 --> 11:51.458
So, what I'm thinking

11:51.541 --> 11:53.750
is maybe, if I really
wanna make a difference,

11:53.833 --> 11:56.333
maybe I get involved
in a great non-profit

11:56.416 --> 11:59.291
and... and I just put journalism
on the back burner

11:59.375 --> 12:01.416
-for a little while.
-That's a great idea.

12:02.083 --> 12:03.083
Yeah.

12:05.625 --> 12:08.583
(WHISPERING) Oh, my God.
That family is...

12:08.666 --> 12:10.791
