always stares at my boobs.

12:15.833 --> 12:17.583
Well...

12:17.666 --> 12:20.458
not as weird as
<i>What Ever Happened to Baby Jane?</i>
over here.

12:20.541 --> 12:22.416
-RACHEL: What?
-Yeah, well...

12:22.500 --> 12:24.750
(MUTTERING) She's coming--
she's coming over to the table.

12:24.833 --> 12:25.625
Hi.

12:25.708 --> 12:26.750
-RACHEL: Hi.
-SHANE PATTON: Hey.

12:26.833 --> 12:28.833
You guys were really
good sports yesterday.

12:28.916 --> 12:31.125
RACHEL: How are you doing?

12:31.208 --> 12:34.166
I don't know. I--
I feel like I failed, but...

12:34.500 --> 12:36.166
Oh, no.

12:36.250 --> 12:38.375
-No.
-TANYA MACQUOID: Yeah.

12:38.458 --> 12:42.375
When I saw my mother's ashes
hit the water, you know,

12:42.458 --> 12:45.666
I just, uh...
It just reminded me of...

12:45.750 --> 12:49.208
of, you know, sprinkling
fish food in an aquarium.

12:49.291 --> 12:53.291
And I was just like,
"Oh, my God," you know?

12:53.375 --> 12:55.958
Am I feeding my mother
to the fishes?

12:56.041 --> 13:00.250
You know? And is that
what she would've wanted?

13:03.750 --> 13:05.125
-SHANE: Uh...
-Just...

13:07.875 --> 13:10.125
Hope you're enjoying
your breakfast.

13:10.208 --> 13:12.041
SHANE: Yeah. Get-- uh, get some.

13:12.625 --> 13:13.916
I think I will.

13:17.625 --> 13:19.750
(LAUGHS)

13:22.416 --> 13:24.833
(DINERS CHATTERING INDISTINCTLY)

13:26.166 --> 13:29.833
Paula, you're not still mad
about that whole Trevor thing,

13:29.916 --> 13:30.958
are you?

13:31.625 --> 13:32.916
No, not at all.

13:34.166 --> 13:38.166
Okay, 'cause if you like a guy,
you can tell me.

13:38.250 --> 13:39.708
Or whatever.
You can trust me.

13:39.791 --> 13:42.750
I'm not gonna, like, swoop him
out from underneath you.

13:43.875 --> 13:46.166
Yeah, I-- I trust you.

13:46.250 --> 13:50.041
Okay, 'cause Trevor was just
like this momentary
lapse of judgment,

13:50.125 --> 13:52.416
and I've learned my lesson.

13:53.916 --> 13:55.291
TANYA: Hey, girls.

13:56.166 --> 13:57.916
Did you get your backpack back?

13:58.000 --> 14:00.541
♪ (SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING) ♪

14:00.625 --> 14:02.708
You left it on the beach
the other day.

14:02.791 --> 14:05.041
I-- I gave it to
one of the beach boys.

14:05.833 --> 14:07.666
-You did?
-Yeah.

14:08.458 --> 14:10.583
I gave it to the one over there.

14:10.666 --> 14:12.583
The one with the khaki face.

14:15.625 --> 14:16.666
