14:24.208 --> 14:25.416
(SIGHS)

14:32.291 --> 14:33.541
-Christie.
-CHRISTIE: Morning.

14:33.625 --> 14:34.541
Hi, ladies.

14:34.625 --> 14:35.875
-GUEST 1: Hello.
-GUEST 2: Hey.

14:36.833 --> 14:38.458
