14:38.541 --> 14:40.125
OLIVIA: Sir. Sir!

14:40.208 --> 14:41.250
Dude.

14:41.333 --> 14:44.000
Oh, aloha.
How is everyone this morning?

14:44.750 --> 14:46.166
You have our backpack.

14:47.875 --> 14:48.791
It's a green backpack.

14:48.875 --> 14:50.375
You said yesterday
that you didn't have it,

14:50.458 --> 14:52.708
but he just said that he
gave it to you two days ago

14:52.791 --> 14:54.583
and then you put it
in the lost and found.

14:54.666 --> 14:56.666
Yeah, I'm pretty sure
it's in your office.

14:58.333 --> 15:00.166
A green backpack?

15:00.250 --> 15:01.958
I-- yes, I do remember that.

15:02.041 --> 15:04.791
I'll-- I'll go to the office
and get it for you right away.

15:07.125 --> 15:08.875
I was thinking that maybe
if I miss journalism,

15:08.958 --> 15:10.541
-then I can just come back--
-SHANE: Hey, man.

15:10.625 --> 15:11.833
Hey, man. Excuse--

15:12.833 --> 15:15.041
-Hey!
-RACHEL: Shane.

15:16.750 --> 15:18.083
-This guy's a fucking puke.
-Shane.

15:18.166 --> 15:19.500
-Did you see that?
-Shane. Shane.

15:19.583 --> 15:21.500
-He fully fucking ignored me.
-I'm trying to talk to you

15:21.583 --> 15:23.500
-about my future.
-I know.

15:25.625 --> 15:28.958
-Okay, yup.
-What do you think of that idea?

15:29.041 --> 15:33.541
Um... I think it's, uh, good.
I think it's cool.

15:38.916 --> 15:41.375
This fucking guy. I'm sorry.
I gotta deal with this.

15:42.000 --> 15:43.000
This is...

15:43.625 --> 15:44.958
Dude?

15:45.041 --> 15:48.083
♪ (UPBEAT MUSIC PLAYING) ♪

16:03.875 --> 16:05.000
Oh, Mr. Patton, good morning.

16:05.083 --> 16:06.541
Did you not see me
in the restaurant just now?

16:06.625 --> 16:08.208
-I'm sorry?
-I'm waving to you,
I'm shouting--

16:08.291 --> 16:10.125
-I know you saw me.
-I was sent to fetch a bag.

16:10.208 --> 16:12.250
You looked right at me
and you kept walking.

16:12.333 --> 16:13.958
My apologies. So sorry.

16:14.041 --> 16:16.208
Oh, how was your
candlelit dinner last night?

16:16.291 --> 16:18.208
(SCOFFS) Yeah, that's what
I wanted to talk to you about.

16:18.291 --> 16:20.666
Uh, it fucking blew, frankly.

16:20.750 --> 16:21.833
-Oh, no.
-Yeah.

16:21.916 --> 16:23.625
You put us on a boat
with a crazy lady

16:23.708 --> 16:26.333
who was having some kind of
fucking memorial service.

16:26.416 --> 16:29.083
You knew! You knew
that she was out there to spread

16:29.166 --> 16:31.166
her dead mother's ashes
on the goddamn ocean.

16:31.250 --> 16:33.000
Oh, well, she might've
mentioned that.

16:33.083 --> 16:35.541
I'm trying to do
a romantic gesture for my wife.

16:35.625 --> 16:36.958
I got a crazy lady
who's having

16:37.041 --> 16:38.958
some kind of fucking
nervous breakdown.

16:39.041 --> 16:40.916
So no, it was not romantic.

16:41.000 --> 16:42.708
It was a dumpster fire
shit show!

16:42.791 --> 16:44.083
I had no idea.

16:44.166 --> 16:47.625
I'm sorry your vacation isn't
everything you'd hoped-- so far.

16:48.166 --> 16:49.416
But the good news,

16:49.500 --> 16:52.541
there's an exciting surprise
you'll be receiving later today.

16:52.625 --> 16:54.916
What? We're gonna get
in our room?

16:55.000 --> 16:56.125
-Unfortunately, no.
-Jesus.

16:56.208 --> 16:58.208
But I think this is really
gonna turn things around.

16:58.291 --> 16:59.875
Then I don't want it!

16:59.958 --> 17:03.208
I don't want a free massage.
I don't want cheap champagne.

17:04.291 --> 17:07.208
What I want is to speak
to your boss.

17:08.625 --> 17:12.208
-Well, I am the resort manager.
-Yeah, but you have a boss.

17:12.291 --> 17:14.041
Who is your boss?

17:14.125 --> 17:17.125
Our general manager, Mr. Zeoli,
is at a conference this week.

17:17.208 --> 17:19.625
Yeah, I want to get
in touch with him.

17:19.708 --> 17:21.708
-Can I have his number?
-I'll have him call you.

17:21.791 --> 17:24.958
No! No. I'm calling him.

17:26.750 --> 17:28.541
I will have someone
bring you his business card

17:28.625 --> 17:30.458
with his cell phone number
to your room.

17:30.541 --> 17:32.750
And you can call him
at your leisure.

17:32.833 --> 17:36.125
Good. This morning, please.

17:37.833 --> 17:41.166
♪ (TENSE MUSIC PLAYING) ♪

17:44.708 --> 17:46.208
Motherfucker!

17:50.000 --> 17:52.875
♪ (TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES) ♪

18:09.916 --> 18:10.916
Shit!

18:21.916 --> 18:23.500
