somebody's phone today.

18:31.166 --> 18:32.958
I can't go another day
without a phone.

18:33.041 --> 18:35.708
You had my phone
all day yesterday.

18:35.791 --> 18:37.541
Okay, can I have it again?

18:37.625 --> 18:38.958
No. I need it.

18:41.375 --> 18:43.375
-Yeah, right.
-No way.

18:45.166 --> 18:46.333
Mom?

18:46.416 --> 18:49.708
Honey, I'd love to help,
but I need to have my phone.

18:49.791 --> 18:51.250
